data.description: Welcome home! This large 5 bedroom, 3.5 bath brick ranch is nestled on almost 1.5 acres with an above ground pool and apple orchard. Also included is a large pole barn with a concrete slab. Amazing kitchen with an oversized island with plenty of storage throughout and stainless steel appliances. Grand master suite with a walk in closet. Updated Pergo flooring in the breakfast nook, living room, hallway and 2 bedrooms.  Family room with a natural brick fireplace.  Spacious unfinished basement with a second natural brick fireplace. Central air 2022.
